summary: This document is an overdraft notice from Fifth Third Bank addressed to Disco Scientia Corporation, indicating that the account was overdrawn on October 9, 2013. It details the account activity leading to the overdraft and the associated fees, urging the corporation to take action to avoid further charges.

persons.name: P. Brian Moore
persons.context: P. Brian Moore is the signatory of the overdraft notice, representing Fifth Third Bank and providing information regarding the account status.

events.title: Account Overdraft
events.description: The account of Disco Scientia Corporation was overdrawn by $46.93, leading to an overdraft fee of $37.00.

keyFacts: The account was overdrawn on October 9, 2013, by $46.93.
An overdraft fee of $37.00 was charged to the account.
The document urges Disco Scientia Corporation to make a deposit by October 15, 2013, to avoid further fees.
The beginning balance on October 9, 2013, was $(37.00).
The ending balance after fees was $(83.93).
